Program: Omnibus
Title: Environment and our behaviour
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376k03
Last Broadcast Date: 17 December 1990
How does the food we eat and the air we breathe affect our behaviour and mental development? A look at the link between food additives and hyperactivity in children, allergies and criminal behaviour and lead in the air with mental health. Contributors include Derek Bryce-Smith.